Metadata.name: Benz Baku F1 City Circuit
Metadata.desc: Track with high speed straights and tight chicanes, inspired by the 2017 Baku F1 City Circuit. A vehicle with a decent top speed and good handling is recommended, note that this is and F1 style track so it will get tight and test your skills. Good luck and remember the words of Colin Mcrae. If In doubt, flat out.  Average Lap is about 1.21, Created by J. Staples
